BACKEND_ARCHITECTURE.md
DEPLOYMENT.md
GITHUB_READY.md
GITHUB_UPLOAD_CHECKLIST.md
SECURITY.md
WINDOWS_SETUP.md
COMMIT_SUMMARY.md

